cent</a><div class="bio">桌游媒介DICE创始人、策展人、艺术设计图书出版人</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/wang-yi-xiang-80-72" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-yi-xiang-80-72'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0f3f68db2e5fb285682896d59a0fe1a0_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="王奕翔"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/zhuoyou/wang-yi-xiang-80-72/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/wang-yi-xiang-80-72" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-yi-xiang-80-72'>王奕翔</a><div class="bio">原創桌遊設計師</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/angelwdx" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$angelwdx'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/41d01506b_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="王宇航"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/zhuoyou/angelwdx/answers" class="answers text-muted">9 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/angelwdx" data-hovercard='p$t$angelwdx'>王宇航</a><div class="bio">智研家文化发展（北京）有限公司 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 市场</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/xiao-da-95-38" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$xiao-da-95-38'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3c43fb0f0d70f037d4363966c044eb11_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="小大"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/zhuoyou/xiao-da-95-38/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/xiao-da-95-38" data-hovercard='p$t$xiao-da-95-38'>小大</a><div class="bio">米宝海豚桌游工作室 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 产品经理</div></div></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="module participants"><div class="module-header"><h3>热门回答者</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items-fulid"><li class="item"><a href="/people/fisher-23" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$fisher-23'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/4abd9edf0_l.jpg" alt="Fisher" class="avatar d50"></a></li><l